<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>A pickup point just opened near you!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #FFF8E7;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #FFFFFF;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
      border-top: 4px solid #D4AF37;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #D4AF37;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .title {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .location-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF8E7 0%, #FAF0E6 100%);
      border: 2px solid #D4AF37;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .location-name {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #D4AF37;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .location-address {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .highlight {
      background-color: #FFF8E7;
      border-left: 4px solid #F4D03F;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #F5F5DC;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">Surespot Eatery</div>
      <h1 class="title">We're now near you! 🎉</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
      <p>Great news! A Surespot pickup point has opened in your area:</p>

      <div class="location-box">
        <div class="location-name">{{locationName}}</div>
        <div class="location-address">{{locationAddress}}</div>
      </div>

      <p>You can now place orders for pickup at this location through the Surespot app. Fresh, delicious food is closer than ever.</p>

      <div class="highlight">
        Open the Surespot app to browse the menu and place your first order from this pickup point.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>You're receiving this because you have a saved address near this pickup point.</p>
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} SureSpot. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
